1. *Namera* mi je da završim fakultet ove godine. (My *intention* is to finish college this year.)
2. Ona je izrazila *nameru* da putuje u Japan. (She expressed her *intention* to travel to Japan.)
3. *Nameravaš* li da dođeš na zabavu? (Are you *planning* to come to the party?)
4. Mi *nameravamo* da kupimo novu kuću u narednom mesecu. (We *intend* to buy a new house next month.)
5. Oni su bili u *nameri* da opljačkaju banku. (They were *intending* to rob the bank.)
6. Da li si *nameravao* da me pozoveš? (Did you *intend* to call me?)
7. Oni su *namerno* ignorisali moje poruke. (They *deliberately* ignored my messages.)
8. *Nemam nameru* da se raspravljam sa tobom. (I have no *intention* of arguing with you.)
9. Moj šef je imao *dobre namere* kada mi je dao otkaz. (My boss had *good intentions* when he fired me.)
10. Bilo je očigledno da je njihova *namera* bila da me izbace iz tima. (It was obvious that their *intent* was to kick me out of the team.)